Title: DUNGEON SOULS
Genre: Action - Adventure - Roguelike
Works on: Windows (7, 8, 10), Mac OS X (10.9+) and Linux (Ubuntu 14.04, Ubuntu 16.04)
Languages: Audio and text: English
Features: single-player - in development
Size: 166 MB
Company: Lamina Studios / Black Shell Media
Rating:	ESRB Rating: Teen (with Blood, Violence)
Store page: https://www.gog.com/game/dungeon_souls

About:
Dungeon Souls is an action-adventure roguelike dungeon crawler which draws heavy inspiration from Nuclear Throne , Risk of Rain, and Overture. Explore vast procedurally generated dungeons, collect loot, and slay hordes of challenging enemies.
Current Updates:
- Harness the powerful abilities of TEN unique characters 
- Explore a plethora of different environments 
- Immerse yourself with deep character progression 
- Experiment with 50+ unique passive items 
- Craft items using Arcane Forge
Future Updates:
- Multiplayer 
- More items 
- New enemies types
- More traps 
- More music 
- More levels

Processor: 2.9 GHz
Memory: 2 GB RAM
Graphics: 256 MB
DirectX: 9.0
Storage 200 MB
Mouse, Keyboard
